name: HELP US
description:
This concept has a very important meaning because it represents a stage that comes for every man or woman. It often happens that the component of faith, not religious but the one inherent in man, is what pulls us out of a tunnel often. But when it also falters and needs help?

This is one of the manipulations I fortunately recovered from my old PC, one autumn day 2019 a friend of mine accidentally formatted my PC making me lose a lot of work files. I managed to recover a few jpegs. This is one of those.

2250 × 2813 150 dpi
